<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, July 7 (Xinhua) -- The Addis Ababa city
administrative council Wednesday approved a tax revenue of 936
million birr (8.121 birr equals to one U.S. dollar) in the coming
1999/2000 budget year starting July 8, 1999.
