<HEADLINE> OAU Membership Fee Arrears 160% of Annual Budget </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Nine members including South Africa, the Central African
Republic, Uganda and Libya, are under sanctions for failing to pay
their membership fees, OAU Spokesman Ibrahim Dagash said at a news
briefing during the two-day OAU ambassadors' meeting which ended
here Wednesday afternoon.
</P>
