650,000th ticket to the third women's World Cup soccer tournament.
An Average of more than 35,000 have attended women's World Cup
soccer matches.
</P>
<P>
"With a sellout of the final, our biggest day is still yet to
come," said Messing, "but I think we can say that the tournament has
been a smashing success."
</P>
<P>
The final will be a rematch of Olympic Games gold medal contest in
which the American team won. But China have been the winners twice in
their three matches against the United States in 1999. 
