Manchester United shirt before his 1989 transfer from Upton Park
to Old Trafford had been sealed.
</P>
<P>
After a successful spell with United he joined Inter Milan
before returning to Britain and signing for Liverpool.
</P>
<P>
The England mid-fielder's future has been thrown into doubt
following Houlier's blunt statement that "Paul Ince is not in my
plans".
</P>
<P>
"I told him that is life. For a player of Paul Ince's profile
it would be difficult for him to be on the bench. It is better
for him to have a fresh challenge," the Anfield boss is reported
as saying.
</P>
