could be postponed if progress was achieved.
</P>
<P>
Thousands of passengers were being trapped at Canada's airports
while the negotiations were going down to the wire. Many changed
their plane tickets while others were waiting for the final
results.
</P>
<P>
As many as 43 international and Canadian airlines promised to
take over passengers from Air Canada in case of failure in
negotiations. 
