<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 8 (Xinhua) -- The Composite Stock Index on the
Shanghai Stock Exchange finished at 1,577.98 points today, up 9.33
points from the previous session, according to the Guangfa
Securities Co. Ltd.
</P>
<P>
The SSE-30 index, based on 30 blue chips selected from more
than 400 A shares for domestic investors on the Shanghai Stock
Exchange, closed at 3,890.81 points, up 14.79 points from the
previous session.
</P>
<P>
A Share Index: 1,674.17 points, up 9.75 points;
</P>
<P>
B Share Index: 49.67 points, up 0.65 points;
</P>
<P>
Total Turnover: 13,535,618,000 yuan;
</P>
<P>
Total Volume: 1,439,775,300 shares. 
</P>
